rows.label: kizunainn060_msg0002
rows.name:
I am told that we may behold a
beautiful vista from the Orl Cloudway
exit in the Liberalitan archipelago.

rows.label: kizunainn060_msg0003
rows.name:
Perhaps it will be a sight
fit for our royal eyes.

rows.label: kizunainn060_msg0004
rows.name:
I command you to transport me there.
Do not tarry with the preparations!
